---
description: Never overwrite .env.local unless the user pastes secret values in the same message
globs: .env.local
alwaysApply: true
---

Do NOT rewrite or reset `.env.local` to empty templates.

- Supabase secrets belong in `.env.supabase` (user-edited).
- Only update env files when the user provides explicit values in the current message.
- Preserve existing OPENAI_API_KEY and VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN when editing env files.
